"""Prevent creation of Undo/Redo chains"""
with pytest.raises(ValueError):
    UndoOperation(cg, user_id='DAU', superseded_operation_id=FakeLogRecords
        .UNDO.id, multicut_as_split=False)
with pytest.raises(ValueError):
    UndoOperation(cg, user_id='DAU', superseded_operation_id=FakeLogRecords
        .REDO.id, multicut_as_split=False)
with pytest.raises(ValueError):
    RedoOperation(cg, user_id='DAU', superseded_operation_id=FakeLogRecords
        .UNDO.id, multicut_as_split=False)
with pytest.raises(ValueError):
    UndoOperation(cg, user_id='DAU', superseded_operation_id=FakeLogRecords
        .REDO.id, multicut_as_split=False)
